        "content": "<p><span aria-label=\"speech balloon\" class=\"emoji emoji-1f4ac\" role=\"img\" title=\"speech balloon\">:speech_balloon:</span> cfallin created <a href=\"https://github.com/bytecodealliance/wasmtime/pull/13347#discussion_r3235402031\">PR review comment</a>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>These new sign-extensions are unfortunate; any way we can avoid them?</p>\n</blockquote>",
